{"tid":1127113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼台灣人說「北京話」當「國語」？","createTime":"2019-04-27T00:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T05:46:42.000Z","uid":226548,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"030fa6a0fca4d7fcdfd85a5be2b9777a86401961","tid":1127113,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:09:07.000Z","msg":"【為什麼挑選這篇文章】<br />\n<br />\n前陣子課綱微調文言文和白話文比例引發一場論戰，但話說回來，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為什麼「北京話」會成為台灣的官方語言</span></strong>、大家所使用的白話文呢？<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>逼迫台灣人放棄母語，把北京話當成自己的官方語言</strong></span>，蔣中正到底在想什麼？<br />\n<br />\n（責任編輯：林芮緹）<br />\n<br />\n為了解決各族群之間無法溝通的問題，國民政府學習西方民族國家統一語言的政策，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在 1913 年將北京的官話定為「國語」</span></strong>，並設計了一套「注音字母」標誌國語發音。因為「字母」兩個字聽起來像是洋人的玩意兒，「注音字母」在 1930 更名為「注音符號」。稱北京方言為「國語」的用法，隨著國民黨來台，便在台灣一直沿用下去，如國中小教科書的語文課本便叫做「國語」或「國文」課本，注音符號也成了小學生學習「國字」的工具。<br />\n<br />\n不過 1920 年代以後，正當白話文運動風起雲湧之際，當時偏左翼、親共產主義的知識份子卻批評以北京話為國語的政策，認為北京話乃是舊時期官僚的口語，是屬於菁英的、統治階層的語言。他們因此提出「大眾語」或「普通話」的概念，認為統一的語言不該以北京話或北京方言為準，而應該融合中國一般民眾的口語，尤其城市裡頭的無產階級的大眾語言，並尊重、保留其他漢族群的口語和少數民族的語言。<br />\n<br />\n但共產黨在 1949 年建立中華人民共和國之後，換了位子也難免換了腦袋，不久便在 1955 年訂出了單一國家語言的政策，依舊以北京的官話作為統一的官方語言，只是不叫「國語」，而是沿用「普通話」一詞。其實， <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">普通話並不普通或普遍，它的來源仍是舊帝制時期清朝官吏所用的北京方言，儘管它的使用人口在眾多語言裡佔最多數。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，兩岸分別<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">使用「國語」與「普通話」，指涉同一種語言：以北京話／官話為標準的中國北方語</span></strong>。對於國家之內多語言的狀態，國民黨與共產黨最終殊途同歸，均是獨尊一種語言而壓抑其他的語言。"},{"pid":"261531301136abf1e4ec526578a0991195045f14","tid":1127113,"uid":17641,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因為台灣人係狗</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900a62f782309e6b4e4d86835f9c78a5e3f5b30b","tid":1127113,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"261531301136abf1e4ec526578a0991195045f14","tid":1127113,"uid":17641,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因為台灣人係狗</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:31:24.000Z","msg":"無得唔講，會罰錢"},{"pid":"d4279577847a6bea514aed13306606c60f71f82b","tid":1127113,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人成日叫自己嗰d先係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3385139430cee3f5567a2939a77769a2c96205","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"d4279577847a6bea514aed13306606c60f71f82b","tid":1127113,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人成日叫自己嗰d先係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題？明明中文就官話文嚟，廣東話就真係唔係中文，你要明白中國人同我哋香港人唔同民族，中國人用中文係理所當然嘅事"},{"pid":"b8299f21cf2b9210fed5330ddfe5c5d73db1c498","tid":1127113,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd3385139430cee3f5567a2939a77769a2c96205","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"d4279577847a6bea514aed13306606c60f71f82b","tid":1127113,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人成日叫自己嗰d先係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題？明明中文就官話文嚟，廣東話就真係唔係中文，你要明白中國人同我哋香港人唔同民族，中國人用中文係理所當然嘅事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"香港用漢字，講粵語，支那人寫殘體中文，講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dbcf7057217f0b95b93cad61743b1fb6d2229d","tid":1127113,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:04:49.000Z","msg":"台港友好！<br />\n總之就兩種語言。不要問，只要信。"},{"pid":"f29305e503da76e691d66c66963afb212be1d523","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a9136e925666d8b1acd53c041ff71639f7828b","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3fa1874bc4fb5c7a111c7b877c9101f52210b8","tid":1127113,"uid":34334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:57:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c6ac0f0e5dada4f4dae05ad6966f8eaca957676","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d3fa1874bc4fb5c7a111c7b877c9101f52210b8","tid":1127113,"uid":34334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd3385139430cee3f5567a2939a77769a2c96205","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"d4279577847a6bea514aed13306606c60f71f82b","tid":1127113,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人成日叫自己嗰d先係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題？明明中文就官話文嚟，廣東話就真係唔係中文，你要明白中國人同我哋香港人唔同民族，中國人用中文係理所當然嘅事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:57:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"無錯，中國人用中國文"},{"pid":"eb46f3a8fa294f26aa16dbb0701ac1b255f67bc1","tid":1127113,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"把契丹韃靼滿洲「胡語」當「國語」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bbbd3c4689b3a13b2a953490945612954cd007","tid":1127113,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:09:51.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅「胡語」，是我們本地中原漢族，或其他本地中原民族稱叫北方草原少數民族所講嘅「北方外族」之方言。<br />\n<br />\n由於我們本地漢族人聽不懂北方外國人之「方言」，「基基姑姑」不明所以言，所以就叫北方外國語言為「胡言亂語」，「胡言」也。"},{"pid":"7b5470c70a5fc067ae7ba5448b17e1958f80b921","tid":1127113,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd3385139430cee3f5567a2939a77769a2c96205","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"d4279577847a6bea514aed13306606c60f71f82b","tid":1127113,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人成日叫自己嗰d先係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題？明明中文就官話文嚟，廣東話就真係唔係中文，你要明白中國人同我哋香港人唔同民族，中國人用中文係理所當然嘅事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"「中文」即係「中國語文」<br />\n<br />\n即係「中國」所用既「語文」<br />\n<br />\n「中國」本身就係一個統戰概念, 「中文」一詞亦然"},{"pid":"66cc00bbbee0ca64ef3f63f10d9f779b93f76940","tid":1127113,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b5470c70a5fc067ae7ba5448b17e1958f80b921","tid":1127113,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd3385139430cee3f5567a2939a77769a2c96205","tid":1127113,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"d4279577847a6bea514aed13306606c60f71f82b","tid":1127113,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人成日叫自己嗰d先係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題？明明中文就官話文嚟，廣東話就真係唔係中文，你要明白中國人同我哋香港人唔同民族，中國人用中文係理所當然嘅事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"「中文」即係「中國語文」<br />\n<br />\n即係「中國」所用既「語文」<br />\n<br />\n「中國」本身就係一個統戰概念, 「中文」